{"tid":922224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"頑皮猩猩搶走自拍棒！牠竟上前制止同伴　還交還給籠外遊客","createTime":"2018-11-30T08:05:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T00:15:47.000Z","uid":66260,"like":324,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"559199b8f2853e6a4391066f29009f0999f7a3a3","tid":922224,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T08:05:50.000Z","msg":"國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n有些動物的聰明行為真的會超乎人類想像！大陸一間野生動物園內的黑猩猩，看到遊客手上的自拍棒，竟趁對方不注意時將它搶走，沒想到牠的同伴見狀後，竟出面阻止牠的霸道行為，並將自拍棒還給在籠子前的遊客，影片曝光後立刻引起網友討論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/11/30/1666431-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F11%2F30%2F1666431-PH.jpg&h=a4324493&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲圖／翻攝自YouTube<br />\n<br />\n根據外媒報導，動物園內的欄舍內有兩隻黑猩猩，其中一隻看到遊客手中的自拍棒，一時興起竟趁機偷拿走並拿在手中把玩，然而，正當前方的遊客不知道該如何是好時，牠的同伴竟走到頑皮猩猩的面前，制止牠的不文明行為，接下來更主動將自拍棒還給人類。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/11/30/1666432-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F11%2F30%2F1666432-PH.jpg&h=3dd02292&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲圖／翻攝自YouTube<br />\n<br />\n而畫面全被一旁的民眾所錄下，影片PO網後引起大批網友討論，紛紛留言大讚猩猩的暖心行為，同時也不捨直呼「這些黑猩猩太聰明，但看到牠的圈養環境，我心都快碎了！」(編輯：張家寧）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3AeM7rCTcHg \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3AeM7rCTcHg%20&d=fTZlYgnirmZfPJI9v7UNyJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=e288812e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3AeM7rCTcHg </a>"},{"pid":"440385c9095a5c03f25c04568ca0891d88bbf419","tid":922224,"uid":142210,"like":267,"dislike":34,"score":233,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T08:08:18.000Z","msg":"睇錯自慰棒"},{"pid":"4fc19fb6e93e1741f9e762d78e09ab44337967fe","tid":922224,"uid":1672,"like":301,"dislike":0,"score":301,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T08:10:14.000Z","msg":"猩猩辱華<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a30d